{"tid":1775173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想問：點解12月6星三單墮樓，好似蘋果/立場都冇報？","createTime":"2019-12-08T16:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T16:28:28.000Z","uid":341689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7d2300f8b1969bc4fa97e6c6edf24867a08e34bc","tid":1775173,"uid":341689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T16:20:48.000Z","msg":"（P牌第一次開post，真心唔知，虛心求教）<br />\n<br />\n3小時內3宗墮樓，好大件事啦。如果係手足或手足家屬被自殺，咁好應該成為今日128文宣啦。但好似唔太多人講？<br />\n<br />\n我Google search 左下，係有頭條日報、01、經濟日報呢啲親中報有報道。<br />\n好似搵唔到蘋果日報、立場有報（？）<br />\n<br />\n唔似係假新聞？<br />\n咁點解冇大肆報道同跟進？<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/12/07/a102724497.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2019%2F12%2F07%2Fa102724497.html&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2LdY%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=7ddf713e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/12/07/a102724497.html</a><br />\n<br />\n這些所謂「自殺」事件均由親共港媒公開報導，警方照例經「初步調查」，在未確定死因的情況下即迅速宣布「無可疑」。<br />\n<br />\n12月6日 三宗「墮樓」<br />\n<br />\n順利邨．樂富．筲箕灣"},{"pid":"4a4af9f8ff6ed4f92e4e8d6be4cfbf0c111dd7c1","tid":1775173,"uid":22796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T16:21:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db187fd36fe1512dead62716a337057c9a2935ee","tid":1775173,"uid":325269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T16:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5PLNMOw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5PLNMOw.jpg&h=0eecb9a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oGcPZ8x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoGcPZ8x.jpg&h=2c118546&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"730d35748737f37843fe72c6f63d905e3c89852c","tid":1775173,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T16:22:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2